2 29, 2025.
3
4 “CAPTIONS
5
6 “SECTION 11. The unit captions used in this 2026 Act are provided
7 only for the convenience of the reader and do not become part of the
8 statutory law of this state or express any legislative intent in the
9 enactment of this 2026 Act.
10
11 “DELAYED OPERATIVE DATE
12
13 “SECTION 12. Section 6 of this 2026 Act and the amendments to
14 ORS 33.055, 33.065, 33.075 and 476.274 by sections 1 to 4 of this 2026 Act
15 become operative on January 1, 2027.
16
17 “EFFECTIVE DATE
18
19 “SECTION 13. This 2026 Act takes effect on the 91st day after the
20 date on which the 2026 regular session of the Eighty-third Legislative
21 Assembly adjourns sine die.”.
